These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: spanish, argentine
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, sailing
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, quad-bike
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the argentine is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | argentine    | spanish |
| Sport         | sailing | basketball    |
| Transport     | scooter     | quad-bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, almond-milk
There are 2 different nationalities: brazilian, indonesian
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the brazilian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk  | coffee   |
| Nationality   | indonesian | brazilian  |
| Transport     | jet-ski   | bus |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: rock-climbing, chess
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, sports
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, skiing
1. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing   | chess  |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | adventure  |
| Sport         | cycling   | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
