The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, satire
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, quad-bike
1. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the person eating cabbage is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Food          | cabbage | kale |
| Movie-Genre   | satire   | zombie   |
| Transport     | quad-bike       | scooter      |

