.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: potato, cauliflower
The people have 2 different jobs:  social-worker, mechanic
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, surfing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the social-worker##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
3. the person eating potato is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | cauliflower | potato     |
| Job     | mechanic | social-worker |
| Sport   | surfing | handball    |

 #################################

 
