.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-14::.
There 2 different types of food: zucchini, eggplant
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, magic-tricks
2 different pets are kept: ferret, horse
1. the owner of the horse is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |
| Food    | eggplant | zucchini  |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | collecting |
| Pet     | ferret  | horse     |

