.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, photography
There are 2 different nationalities: indonesian, italian
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, rabbit
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
2. the indonesian is on the left of the italian##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | photography | camping |
| Nationality   | indonesian     | italian     |
| Pet           | rabbit          | goldfish     |

